{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"518a696844","title":"关于武斗的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"08e29d6990","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"518a696844"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4abd09c80f","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶极专政下革命的主要对象","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"7a94e6f1df","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年八月）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"94066397f0","type":"paragraph","text":"在无产阶级专政下革命的主要对象，是脂藏在无产阶级专政机构内部的资产阶级司合部；我们就是对无产阶级专政机构内部的这一部分进行革命。从我们党和我们国家的整体来说，它们是不占统治地位的，但是必须打倒他们，才能巩固和强化无产阶级专政，防止资本主义复辟。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"dc9e13688d","type":"paragraph","text":"转摘自《红旗》杂志一九六七年第十三期社论","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"047056c5f5","type":"paragraph","text":"《彻底播毁资产阶级司合部——纪念党的","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"f009c6b638","type":"paragraph","text":"八届十一中全会召开一周年》关于武斗的指示","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"3ca0a0207f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年八月）","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"64929af0ea","type":"paragraph","text":"对武斗不要看得太紧张，对形势不能看得太严重，不要急。那里有武斗，必然有后台，让他多表演一下，越表演越孤立，使群众看得更清楚，群众孤立他，就好办了。乱是暂时的，可以转化为好的。打架是支流，是暂时的支流。决不能转移斗争的大方向。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"d23a7bc807","type":"paragraph","text":"对《中共中央、国务院、中央重委、中央交革小粗给煤炭工业战线职工的一","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"fadd4bffe3","type":"paragraph","text":"封信》的批示和修改","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"bf69873c17","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年八月十六日）批示：已开，照办。","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"332908c7df","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东主要修改：","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"c25af7b537","type":"paragraph","text":"信的开头，“广大的职工群众们”一句是主席加的。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"9d7a6a09ea","type":"paragraph","text":"信的第七段，在“无产阶级革命派和革命职工必须把国家利签”一句后加了“工人阶级利签”只字。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"7587deda05","type":"paragraph","text":"第八段“凡是坚持下去、坚持生产，做出成绩的职工，不论属于哪个群众组织或者未参加组织，都应当给予表扬和适当奖励。”整段都是主席新加进去的。","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"},{"id":"161f3de39e","type":"paragraph","text":"·323","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844"}],"page":{"id":"34dbca93f4","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"518a696844","start":336,"end":336}}}},"__N_SSG":true}